        <td><span class=notes>$ifids[0]</span></td></tr>";
    for ($i = 1 ; $i < count($ifids) ; $i++)
        echo "<tr><td></td><td><span class=notes>$ifids[$i]</span></td></tr>";
    echo "</table>";
}
