             $j < count($inrefs) && $inrefs[$j]['reftype'] == $x['reftype'] ;
             $j++) ;

        $cnt = $j - $i;
        if ($cnt > 1) {
            echo "<span class=notes>" . initCap($x['tonames'])
                . ":</span><br><div class=\"indented\">";
